    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:18px;">A Certified ProAdvisor fixes the feed and the books behind it.</h2>
    <div class="prose">
      <p>Reconnecting a feed is the easy part. The work that actually restores trust in the numbers is everything the broken feed left behind: removing duplicate downloads without deleting real transactions, recovering the gap of missing dates, re-categorizing what came in wrong, and re-running reconciliation until each month ties to the bank statement again. A Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor with active Online and Desktop certifications does that against a written scope and verifies the feed is stable before closing. Independent firm &mdash; not Intuit, and not Intuit&rsquo;s software support; an Intuit account, login, or billing matter stays with Intuit.</p>
